{"tid":1696540,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[Sir This Way] 北歐有風向想幫香港同中國談判! 麻煩幫手Comment + Share","createTime":"2019-11-06T08:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T14:19:28.000Z","uid":160131,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"441d6a40d9c95b4fc4dda24b1c3158a1bcbb193b","tid":1696540,"uid":160131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"北歐國家一向以人權自由見稱, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上星期五<ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">丹麥國會外交事務委員會用左一個鐘就香港議題質詢外交部部長</span></ins>,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全丹麥文但都post下條link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.dk/udvalg/udvalgene/URU/kalender/45623/samraad.htm?fbclid=IwAR3q3tA7NDC8Xw00eiiNLUC-7aBLkaMTFEdiJmrL0KigGVHsTRc7mjzKnTQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.dk%2Fudvalg%2Fudvalgene%2FURU%2Fkalender%2F45623%2Fsamraad.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3q3tA7NDC8Xw00eiiNLUC-7aBLkaMTFEdiJmrL0KigGVHsTRc7mjzKnTQ&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=26b51c88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.dk/udvalg/udvalgene/URU/kalender/45623/samraad.htm?fbclid=IwAR3q3tA7NDC8Xw00eiiNLUC-7aBLkaMTFEdiJmrL0KigGVHsTRc7mjzKnTQ</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然外交部部長依然唔肯正面回應,<br />\n但係會議之後有國會議員同大學教授向我地表示,<br />\n想聯合其他北歐國家, 幫香港發聲做和事佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: teal;\">手足們依家忙緊翻譯, 好快有片睇</span></ins>!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實丹麥有唔少政治人物關注緊香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n本地人都不斷發起活動講香港同中國既情況,<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望各地手足係專注美國英國之餘,<br />\n都花少少時間comment下RT下北歐既消息,</span></span></strong><br />\n等我地依班唔係香港既手足有多d籌碼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今次希望大家follow同多謝既兩個人:</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n社會自由黨中國評論員Thomas Rohden<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DenmarkSupportingHongKong/videos/491673084762795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDenmarkSupportingHongKong%2Fvideos%2F491673084762795&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=37ec082d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DenmarkSupportingHongKong/videos/491673084762795</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thomasrohden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthomasrohden&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=1d628350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thomasrohden</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟議員Margrete Auken<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DenmarkSupportingHongKong/videos/528214677961110/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDenmarkSupportingHongKong%2Fvideos%2F528214677961110%2F&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=3f8dde58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DenmarkSupportingHongKong/videos/528214677961110/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/margreteauken\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmargreteauken&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=09aa76cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/margreteauken</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">兄弟爬山, 一齊努力!</span></div></strong>"},{"pid":"ca9dbb93f4b9d5e1d6f13f1f868362b1de0706d7","tid":1696540,"uid":13474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"11月9日：7區開花！香港人反抗！<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689356</a>"},{"pid":"303431c8a89f573c920f305463f908f959ea382f","tid":1696540,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d163778824767d2c8f965d8688cf155adae47c","tid":1696540,"uid":81879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a2efa44054fc9fd86d43bf211e8819e13c9a5e0","tid":1696540,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9558ee0128cd8eddf3157fc1749f6ee24eb38a45","tid":1696540,"uid":217080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605922e05071eb9d1b4f9f1556789c278685eff7","tid":1696540,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4fe4b128e7eb0442c8295d7e64591cd0a26b42e","tid":1696540,"uid":70771,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8a2efa44054fc9fd86d43bf211e8819e13c9a5e0","tid":1696540,"uid":77788,"like":1,"dislike":36,"score":-35,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"見到你個回覆, 再望一望你個名<br />\n哦, 明晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cl